data.description: Beautiful craftsman-style home in the sought after neighborhood of Mistletoe Heights! This home includes a large covered porch, 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and the original fireplace. Original wood floors and windows throughout.  Walking distance to Lily B Clayton Elementary.  Near FW Zoo, entertainment and museum district, and hospital district.  Property also includes a guest house that is currently rented. Market rent for similar ADU Guest House properties in the area is $900-$975. Ready for new owners to make this one your own!
